task.summary: Displays a list of books with authors and publishing dates
Displays list of books only after menu selection
Displays error message if the menu option is invalid.
Adds quit to the menu options

Fixes a command reading bug
Allows the test to add multiple commands. The implementation of command reading in Biblioteca now calls read only once.
Extracts main() into a App class
Fixes display spacing issue for menu
Removes input from Biblioteca and adds it to App
Listens to user input continuously until quit
Refactors Menu Strings into a Menu Class
Creates a Commands Enum and extracts it and Menu Options class from App
